description:
The image displays a presentation slide focused on "AI-powered fraud detection." The main subject is a graph illustrating two lines representing detection performance over time: one line (blue) indicates performance with AI, while the other (pink) shows performance without AI. The slide indicates several key statistics: 

- "8X faster recovery time" and "7X higher detection accuracy" are highlighted next to each corresponding line, emphasizing the benefits of using AI technology.
- Additionally, "14X longer deterrence" is mentioned, suggesting a significant improvement in sustained fraud detection effectiveness when employing AI.

The backdrop of the slide has a modern, digital design with a grid pattern, likely to reflect a tech-centric theme. To the right of the graph, light decorative elements can be seen, possibly indicating a formal presentation setting. Overall, the slide aims to convey the advantages of AI in fraud detection clearly and visually.
